snippet.title: Black The Fall | Release Date Reveal Trailer | Square Enix Collective | PEGI
snippet.description:
We are pleased announced that Black The Fall is coming to Steam, PS4 and Xbox One on July 11th! 

Add to your Steam wishlist now: http://store.steampowered.com/app/308060/Black_The_Fall/
